EN: Your throat seems a little hoarse.
ZH: 我的嗓子很干燥。
EN: My throat is very dry.
ZH: 他的嗓子发炎了。
EN: His throat is inflamed.
ZH: 她的嗓子非常痛。
EN: Her throat is very painful.
ZH: 请不要大声喊，不然会伤到你的嗓子。
EN: Please don't shout loudly, or you will hurt your throat.
ZH: 这种药可以缓解嗓子疼痛。
EN: This medicine can relieve sore throat.
ZH: 他的嗓子不舒服，所以不愿多说话。
EN: His throat isn't comfortable, so he doesn't want to talk much.
ZH: 对于唱歌来说，嗓子是最重要的器官。
EN: For singing, the throat is the most important organ.
ZH: 她总是为了保护自己的嗓子而戴着围巾。
EN: She always wears a scarf to protect her throat.
ZH: 当他感觉嗓子不舒服时，会喝点温水。
EN: When he feels discomfort in his throat, he will drink some warm water.
ZH: 我的嗓子有点痒，可能是感冒了。
EN: My throat is a bit itchy, maybe I caught a cold.
ZH: 我昨晚一直咳嗽，现在我的嗓子很痛。
EN: I coughed all night last night, now my throat hurts a lot.
ZH: 我用了抗生素治好了嗓子发炎。
EN: I used antibiotics to treat the inflamed throat.
ZH: 她的嗓子突然变得沙哑了。
EN: Her voice suddenly became hoarse.
ZH: 预防感冒最好的方法是多喝热水，保持嗓子湿润。
EN: The best way to prevent a cold is to drink plenty of warm water and keep your throat moist.
